@page "/documentation/self-hosted"

<PageTitle>Self-Hosted Docs - XNet›</PageTitle>


<main class="container-apple main-page">
    <div class="doc-wrapper">
        <DocSidebar />
        <div class="doc-main-content animate-fade">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white mb-4">Self-Hosted Server</h1>
            
            <div class="glass-card border-success-subtle p-3 mb-5 d-flex align-items-center" style="background: rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.1);">
                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success fs-4 me-3"></i>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="h6 text-white fw-bold mb-1">Production Ready: XNet Hub v1.0</h4>
                    <p class="small text-sf-secondary m-0">The Self-Hosted Synchronization Hub is now available with full support for cross-platform data consistency.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p class="hero-description mb-5">The XNet Synchronization Hub is a high-performance, private server designed to act as the central brain for your distributed network operations. Built on ASP.NET Core and SQLite, it provides a lightweight but robust infrastructure for modern engineers.</p>

            <div class="doc-section mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 text-white mb-3">Core Capabilities</h2>
                <div class="row g-4 mt-2">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="p-4 rounded-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
                            <h4 class="text-white h5 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-2 text-info"></i> Security</h4>
                            <p class="text-sf-secondary small m-0">Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) and encrypted storage for all sensitive session credentials and terminal logs.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="p-4 rounded-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
                            <h4 class="text-white h5 mb-3"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat me-2 text-success"></i> Sync Engine</h4>
                            <p class="text-sf-secondary small m-0">Advanced synchronization protocol supporting "Push" and "Merge" strategies for NetBox objects and device inventory.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="doc-section mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 text-white mb-3">Deployment Guide</h2>
                <p class="text-sf-secondary">Setting up your private Hub is straightforward and designed for simplicity.</p>
                <div class="mt-4 ms-2">
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="badge bg-white text-dark rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;">1</div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="text-white h6 mb-1">Clone & Build</h5>
                            <p class="text-sf-secondary small">Navigate to <code>XNet.SelfHosted</code> and run <code>dotnet build</code> to prepare the server binaries.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="badge bg-white text-dark rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;">2</div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="text-white h6 mb-1">Configuration</h5>
                            <p class="text-sf-secondary small">Adjust the <code>appsettings.json</code> to point to your desired storage path. The system defaults to a local SQLite instance for Zero-Config deployment.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-3">
                        <div class="badge bg-white text-dark rounded-circle d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 24px; height: 24px;">3</div>
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="text-white h6 mb-1">Client Pairing</h5>
                            <p class="text-sf-secondary small">In the macOS XNet app, go to Settings > Synchronization and enter your Server URL. Use the generated API key for secure pairing.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="doc-section mb-5">
                <h2 class="h3 text-white mb-3">Architecture</h2>
                <div class="p-4 rounded-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
                    <ul class="text-sf-secondary small list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-cpu me-2"></i> <strong>Runtime:</strong> .NET 10 (Next-Gen)</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-database me-2"></i> <strong>Storage:</strong> SQLite with Entity Framework Core</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-hdd-network me-2"></i> <strong>API Strategy:</strong> RESTful with Bearer Token Auth</li>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-window-sidebar me-2"></i> <strong>Dashboard:</strong> Blazor Interactive Server</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
